## ===== ACL SECTION =====

! NTP ACL (allow mgmt VLAN)
ip access-list standard NTP-MGMT
 permit 10.10.199.0 0.0.0.255
 deny any
exit

## ===== NTP SETTINGS =====
clock timezone CET 1
clock summer-time CEST recurring

! Use correct source for outgoing NTP packets
ntp source GigabitEthernet0/0/0

! Sync from R1 (R1 → R2)
ntp server 10.10.100.1

! ACL for who may query NTP (mgmt VLAN)
ntp access-group serve-only NTP-MGMT
ntp access-group query-only NTP-MGMT
end


